# devices.conf — map each machine's hostname to an emoji + label.
# Format: hostname_glob|emoji|label   (one per line, '#' comments allowed)
# The hook matches `hostname` against the glob in order; first match wins.
#
# Copy this to devices.conf and edit. Single-machine users can skip the file
# entirely and instead set TELEGRAM_DEVICE_EMOJI / TELEGRAM_DEVICE_LABEL in env.

my-laptop*|💻|laptop
my-desktop*|🖥|desktop
my-server*|🏭|server
*|📱|unknown
